Subject: MacOS 15 support
Description:
We'd like to begin testing the new version of MacOS but so far EPP is our only agent that has not explicitly announced support for the new OS.  I know on my previous ticket your engineering team said there would be day 1 support but the agent update dashboard still does not show support for 10.15 and I haven't seen any notice from your team either.

Is there an ETA for when this support will be added so that we can begin testing?
Solution_Comment__c: Informed customer that the latest version of the agent is compatible with MACOS 15
